{"tid":705242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車Cam直擊】勵德邨情侶拍拖過路 女友畀的士撞低","createTime":"2018-06-17T03:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T15:48:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95c014c317e8ffd369a1a75e644cf5eb6f185ede","tid":705242,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423348&d=jjdqWrL2%2FrHOZXlUUn0K2I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a2a86edf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423348&h=081f6dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423348</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月17日 <br />\n<br />\n【車Cam直擊】勵德邨情侶拍拖過路<br />\n女友畀的士撞低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一輛的士昨晨2時許，接載一名女乘客往北角勵德邨，的士抵埗入閘不遠，一對情侶橫過馬路，兩人背向的士，而司機又沒有察覺有人過路，收掣不及右車頭將女子撞倒。<br />\n<br />\n據的士車Cam顯示，男子見女友被撞低，氣憤衝前向司機指駡，司機連忙道歉講「對唔住」。幸女事主傷勢不重，救護員到場包紮及送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n肇事姓陳61歲司機稱，任的士司機20多年，第一次遇到撞傷人意外。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n政府被插「助攻」電子煙　全面禁煙要學一地兩檢？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n紅隧3車撞2傷　往香港全封半小時"},{"pid":"1cb0081db3f98283b7c807cf15d0f4d47fd7f1d4","tid":705242,"uid":77569,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80c0512e8eca05063b997f1f821ba4a1653efdc0","tid":705242,"uid":172379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bd038dfa48d94ce7ca32f3982ebfabe40019e71","tid":705242,"uid":112583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"見條女冇咩事<br />\n司機未落車己經講哂對唔住，己經好好多<br />\n<br />\n好多司機撞完車真係匿係車玩電話， 嬲撚到你想拖佢落車打"},{"pid":"7c533c7094c222f22b60e8479857aec04273d7e8","tid":705242,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc